Author: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date:   Sun Mar 1 15:15:36 2026 +0000

    feat: deep Genesis key integration ΓÇö retrieval, DB, event bus, TimeSense, mirror feed
    
    Genesis tracking added to:
      - RAG retrieval (every search gets a key with query, chunks found, top score)
      - DB session errors (every OperationalError tracked with type/message)
      - All Genesis keys now publish 'genesis.key_created' on event bus
        (fixes central_orchestrator subscription mismatch)
    
    TimeSense integration:
      - Added get_context() alias for now_context() (fixes mirror/qwen-net API mismatch)
      - Component health map now includes time_context (period, business_hours, day_of_week)
    
    Event bus fixes:
      - genesis.key_created now published alongside genesis.{key_type}
      - system.health_changed published when component status transitions
    
    Mirror self-model integration:
      - New /api/component-health/mirror-feed endpoint provides:
        component statuses, problems, activity patterns, temporal context
      - Designed for mirror to observe and reflect on system behavior
    
    Closed-loop observability chain:
      Genesis keys ΓåÆ Event bus ΓåÆ Component health ΓåÆ Mirror ΓåÆ Self-healing
    
    Co-authored-by: aaron031291 <aaron031291@users.noreply.github.com>
